title Run 2: Incremental Update  (Jul-Dec 2022)

start
:New parquet file arrives in data/\n**2 files, 2000 reviews total** (Jan-Dec 2022);

:**raw_reviews**\nReads all parquet files (both H1 + H2)\nReplaces the table: now **2000 rows**;
note right
  Same 3 quality checks as Run 1.
